dren's television show ''[[Chigley]]'' || || \n|- \n| Brabinger || family retainer of the fforbes-Hamiltons from the [[BBC]] TV series ''[[To the Manor Born]]'' || [[John Rudling]] || \n|- \n| Fritz Brenner || [[Nero Wolfe]]'s servant ||  || \n|- \n| Brewster || the Cranleighs\u2019 butler in ''[[Doctor Who]]'' \u2013 ''[[Black Orchid (Doctor Who)|Black Orchid]]'' || [[Brian Hawksley]] || \n|- \n| Brian Albumen || faithful servant/valet to Quadruple Professor Adonis Cnut ([[Rik Mayall]]) from the [[ITV (TV network)|ITV]] TV series ''[[Believe Nothing]]'' || [[Michael Maloney]] || \n|- \n| Brown, Birmingham || butler/chauffeur of Charlie Chan in the 1940s film serial || [[Mantan Moreland]] || \n|- \n| Brunton || butler to the Musgrave family in ''[[The Adventure of the Musgrave Ritual]]'' || [[James Hazeldine]], [[Brian Jackson (actor)|Brian Jackson]], [[David Bannerman (actor)|David Bannerman]], [[Clifton Boyne]] || \n|-  \n| [[Mervyn Bunter]] || valet of [[Lord Peter Wimsey]] in several novels and short-stories by [[Dorothy Leigh Sayers]] (see also [[Batman (military)]]) || [[Glyn Houston]], [[Richard Morant]], [[Derek Newark]], [[Charles Lloyd-Pack]], [[Ronald Adam (actor)|Ronald Adam]], [[Seymour Hicks]], [[Aubrey Mather]] || \n|- \n| Butler, Domovoi || from the ''[[Artemis Fowl (series)|Artemis Fowl]]'' novels || ||\n|- \n| Butler, Juliet || from the ''Artemis Fowl'' novels || ||\n|- \n| Butler, The || in ''[[The Adventures of Jimmy Neutron]]'', a holographic butler that Jimmy makes, later destroyed when Jimmy's dad removes the power pack, causing an explosion || [[Corey Burton]] || \n|- \n| Butler, The || butler to No. 2 in ''[[The Prisoner]]'' || [[Angelo Muscat]] || \n|- \n| Butler Livers || butler from the game ''[[Brave Fencer Musashi]]'' || [[R. Martin Klein]] || \n|- \n| Mr. Butlertron || from ''[[Clone High]]'' || Chris Miller || <ref>[https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0588087/ Chris Miller]</ref> \n|- \n| Charles Carson || Butler to the Crawley family in the 