ck McCann]] || \n|- \n| [[Edgar]] || butler to retired opera diva Madame Adelaide Bonfamille in ''[[The Aristocats]]'' || [[Roddy Maude-Roxby]] || \n|- \n| [[Mr. E. Blackadder|Edmund Blackadder]] || butler to the Prince of Wales in ''[[Blackadder#Series 3: Blackadder the Third|Blackadder the Third]]'' || [[Rowan Atkinson]] || \n|- \n| English || butler to Kid Notorious in ''[[Kid Notorious]]'' || Alan Selka ||\n|-\n| Emilio Lopez || butler to Preston Blake in ''[[Mr. Deeds]]'' || [[John Turturro]] ||\n|- \n| Ferguson || butler to [[Frasier Crane]] in ''[[Frasier]]'' episode \"[[Taking Liberties (Frasier)#ep173|Taking Liberties]]\" || [[Victor Garber]] || \n|- \n| Claude Fitzwilliam || butler to Victoria Woodworth in ''[[Fitzwilly]]'' || [[Dick Van Dyke]] ||\n|-\n| Fodor || butler to the Mortevals in [[Boris Karloff]] Mexican film ''[[House of Evil]]'' || [[Jos\u00e9 Luis G. de Le\u00f3n]] || \n|- \n| Franz || butler to the Von Trapp family in ''[[The Sound of Music]]'' || Gil Stuart || \n|- \n| Mr. French || Uncle Bill's butler in the 1960s US sitcom ''[[Family Affair]]'' || [[Sebastian Cabot (actor)|Sebastian Cabot]] || \n|- \n| Frith || Butler to the De Winter family || [[Edward Fielding]], [[Hugh Morton (actor)|Hugh Morton]], [[John Horsley (actor)|John Horsley]] || \n|- \n| Genji Ronoue || from ''[[Umineko no Naku Koro ni]]'' || || \n|- \n| Geoffrey Butler || from ''[[The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air]]'' (Joseph Marcell also plays the recurring role of Massimo Marone's butler on ''[[The Bold and the Beautiful]]'', who used to work for a family in Beverly Hills, a reference to his role on ''Fresh Prince'') || [[Joseph Marcell]]|| \n|- \n| George (billed as Manservant) || manservant to [[Damien Thorn]] in ''[[Omen III: The Final Conflict]]'' || [[Hugh Moxey]] || \n|- \n| [[George Costanza]] || briefly became [[Frank Costanza]]'s butler in ''[[The Handicap Spot]]'' due to payment of a wrecked car || [[Jason Alexander]] || \n|- \n| Giles || from the murder mystery realit