]], [[Jackie Chan]] || \n|- \n| Paul Moriyama || Momoka Nishizawa's butler in ''[[Sgt. Frog]]'' || || \n|- \n| Peppermint Butler || Princess Bubblegum's butler in ''[[Adventure Time]]'' ||[[Steve Little (actor)|Steve Little]]|| \n|- \n| Pfister || Butler in Haunted Honeymoon'' ||[[Bryan Pringle]]|| \n|- \n| Plimpton || Butler to Dr. Wilfred Glendon || Joseph North ||\n|-\n| Poole || Butler to Dr. Henry Jekyll in ''[[The Strange Case of Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde]]'' || [[George Stevens (actor)|George Stevens]], [[Edgar Norton]], [[Peter Godfrey (director)|Peter Godfrey]], [[Gillie Fenwick]], [[Stanley Holloway]], [[Roland Curram]], [[Frank Barrie]], [[Donald Grody]], [[Peter Johl]], [[James Judy]], [[Arnold Pinnock]], [[Brian Pettifer]] || \n|- \n| Pork || Butler and valet to Gerald O'Hara || [[Oscar Polk]] || \n|- \n| Praiseworthy || [[Jeeves]]-like butler in the children's novel ''[[By the Great Horn Spoon!]]'' by [[Sid Fleischman]] || || \n|- \n| Ramsley || from ''[[The Haunted Mansion]]'' || [[Terence Stamp]] || \n|-\n| Raunce || succeeds to the position from [[footman]] when Eldon the Butler dies, in the novel ''[[Loving (novel)|Loving]]'' by [[Henry Green]] || ||\n|- \n| Randolph || The Cleary's Butler from ''[[Wedding Crashers]]'' || [[Ron Canada]] || \n|- \n| Raymond || Butler and valet to [[Charles Foster Kane]] || [[Paul Stewart (actor)|Paul Stewart]] || \n|- \n| Reginald || The Quartermaine family's former butler in the TV series ''[[General Hospital]]'' || || \n|- \n| Riff-Raff || Butler and handyman to [[The Rocky Horror Show|Dr. Frank-N-Furter]] in ''[[The Rocky Horror Show]]'' and the film adaptation ''[[The Rocky Horror Picture Show]]'' || [[Richard O'Brien]], [[Raul Esparza]], [[Sebastian Bach]], [[Mark Price (actor)|Mark Price]], [[Jason Wooten]] || \n|- \n| Riffael Raffit || in ''[[Godchild]]'' || || \n|- \n| Riffael Valentine || Butler for Lucien Ebanezer of the Ebanezer Household in Kuroshitsuji III fanmade || || \n|- \n| Rihito Shibata || Mei Shinon