e]] (English) || \n|- \n| various members of the [[Igor (Discworld)|Igor family]] || in the ''[[Discworld]]'' novels || || \n|-\n|Vishnal\n|butler to the avatar in [[Rune Factory 4]]\n|[[Vic Mignogna]] (English), [[Daisuke Namikawa]] (Japanese)\n|\n|-\n|Volkanon\n|butler to the avatar in [[Rune Factory 4]]\n|[[Patrick Seitz]] (English), [[Yukitoshi Hori]] (Japanese)\n|\n|- \n| Wadsworth || in the movie ''[[Clue (film)|Clue]]'' || [[Tim Curry]] || \n|- \n| [[Hellsing#Walter C. Dornez|Walter C. Dornez]] || from the manga ''[[Hellsing]]'' (and subsequent [[anime]]) by [[Kouta Hirano]] || [[Motomu Kiyokawa]], [[Romi Park]] (young) || \n|- \n| Wallace || the Ridgemeres\u2019 butler in the ''[[Only Fools and Horses]]'' episode \"[[A Touch of Glass]]\" || [[Donald Bisset]] || \n|- \n| Wilkins || Butler to Mr. and Mrs. Topper || [[Alan Mowbray]] || \n|- \n| Willikins || [[Samuel Vimes]]' butler in the ''[[Discworld]]'' novels by [[Terry Pratchett]] || || \n|- \n| Winston || from ''[[Oliver & Company]]'' || || \n|- \n| Winston || the Griplings\u2019 butler and chauffeur from ''[[As Told By Ginger]]'' || [[John Kassir]] || \n|- \n| Winter || Butler to Sam Flusky || [[Jack Watling]], [[Jim Holt (actor)|Jim Holt]] ||\n|-\n| [[Waylon Smithers]] ||assistant to Mr Burns from ''[[The Simpsons]]'' || [[Harry Shearer]] || \n|- \n|[[Wintergreen (comics)|Wintergreen]] || [[Deathstroke|Slade]]'s butler in ''[[Teen Titans (animated series)|Teen Titans]]'' || || \n|- \n| [[List_of_Archer_characters#woodhouse|Woodhouse]] || Sterling Archer's mistreated butler  (technically a valet) in the comedy series ''[[Archer (2009 TV series)|Archer]]'', who formerly worked for Mallory Archer. || [[George Coe]] || \n|- \n| [[Wong (comics)|Wong]] || from [[Marvel Comics]]' ''[[Doctor Strange]]'' series || || \n|- \n| You There ||butler to [[Bender Bending Rodr\u00edguez|Bender's]] Uncle Vladimir in ''[[Futurama]]'' episode \"[[The Honking]]\" || || \n|- \n|[[List of The Lion King characters#Zazu|Zazu]] 